ght.  The BOM sees that Jokes Knightly has a “joke book” that turns out to be the BOOK OF BETRAYAL.  That's how Mike Knight has become so funny – by stealing everyone's material!  BOM calls in Magmar, who saves him from Mike Knight AND takes the Book of Betrayal.  As Jestro comes off-stage to great applause, the BOM tells him they have the Book of Betrayal.  The BOM calls in Magmar and his monsters and they start a fight as Clay comes to Jestro's defense and calls on the other Knights for backup.  A big battle ensues that destroys the comedy club in Funnyton.  The Knights win and drive-off Magmar, the monsters and the BOM.  As they retreat, the BOM looks around: “Where's my Jestro?!”  Jestro sneaked away during the fight and is in a nearby forest with…the Book of Betrayal.</desc>
