e Book of Betrayal!  He looms over Clay, about to consume him, too, and make him into Monstrux!  Suddenly, Robin appears carrying TECHKALIBER…he tosses it to Clay.  Just as the huge Book of Monsters falls on Clay, he holds up Techkaliber and Merlok 2.0 is there…his full power in the sword.  Clay sticks the sword into the Book of Monster's huge mouth.  BOOM!  There's a BIG, MAGICAL EXPLOSION!  As we cut back inside, we see the Book of Monsters is gone.  The Knights release Clay and he thanks them and Jestro for saving him.  Jestro thanks them all for saving him and seeing the good in him.  WE DISSOLVE TO: The JoustDome.  In a final ceremony the King and Queen reward the knights and congratulate them for keeping the kingdom safe.  There are speeches, happiness and friendship.  And Jestro even does a bit that's funny.  At the very end we see a hint of something…Monstrux and the Book of Monsters are still out there.</desc>
